iframeEmbedDescription: Embed your map using the <iframe> tag. This option works best for content management systems that don't support a native HTML embed.
mapViewTooltip: Choose how this map appears across different screen sizes:
permissionsNoticeDescription: Viewers will need to sign in with appropriate credentials to see this map and its contents.
preserveScaleTooltip: Opens the map at the saved scale, preserving the relative size of features across devices. Otherwise, the scale varies to show the features in the saved extent.
scriptEmbedDescription: Embed your map directly into the HTML of your website using the Maps SDK for JavaScript.
sizeInfo: Sizes are responsive and based on browser window height and width
